Elections are over, get back to work!

Posted by darrellnorton on November 3, 2004

I’ve remained quiet on the political front, allowing others to show either their ignorance or brilliance depending on whom they supported in relation to your candidate.


All I have to say is that Kerry went out with class (unlike his predecessor), and the American population woke up with a record turnout. Now let’s all work on unity, as both President Bush and Senator Kerry called for!


Oh, and if you didn’t vote this year, please do so next time!
